f2 = read.csv("m1.csv")
library(ggplot2)
o1=f2$m1
o2=f2$m2
o3=f2$m3
o4=f2$m4
o5=f2$m5

df1 = data.frame(
  length=o1,
  index=c(1:length(o1))
)
df2 = data.frame(
  length=o2,
  index=c(1:length(o2))
)
df3 = data.frame(
  length=o3,
  index=c(1:length(o3))
)
df4 = data.frame(
  length=o4,
  index=c(1:length(o4))
)
df5 = data.frame(
  length=o5,
  index=c(1:length(o5))
)

dataset = data.frame(
  df1,df2,df3,df4,df5
)

k1=f2$k1
k2=f2$k2
k3=f2$k3
k4=f2$k4
k5=f2$k5
Df1 = data.frame(
  length=k1,
  index=c(1:length(k1))
)
Df2 = data.frame(
  length=k2,
  index=c(1:length(k2))
)
Df3 = data.frame(
  length=k3,
  index=c(1:length(k3))
)
Df4 = data.frame(
  length=k4,
  index=c(1:length(k4))
)
Df5 = data.frame(
  length=k5,
  index=c(1:length(k5))
)

Dataset = data.frame(
  Df1,Df2,Df3,Df4,Df5
)

ggplot(df1,aes(x=index,y=length))+
  geom_point()
ggplot(df2,aes(x=index,y=length))+
  geom_point()
ggplot(df3,aes(x=index,y=length))+
  geom_point()
ggplot(df4,aes(x=index,y=length))+
  geom_point()
ggplot(df5,aes(x=index,y=length))+
  geom_point()

ggplot(dataset,aes(x=index,y=length))+
  geom_point(aes(x=index,y=length),color="red",alpha=.6,pch=16,size=3)+
  geom_point(aes(x=index.1,y=length.1),color="blue",alpha=.6,pch=17,size=4)+
  geom_point(aes(x=index.2,y=length.2),color="black",alpha=.6,pch=18,size=3)+
  geom_point(aes(x=index.3,y=length.3),color="orange",alpha=.6,pch=19,size=4)+
  geom_point(aes(x=index.4,y=length.4),color="green",alpha=.6,pch=20,size=3)+
  labs(x="竹节数",y="长度/单位(cm)")+
  ggtitle("木本竹样本竹节~竹节长关系")+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks=seq(0, 16, 1))+
  scale_y_continuous(breaks=seq(0, 30, 5))+
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5))
